{"tid":379912,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來你一直都唔信我...","createTime":"2017-08-29T17:06:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-30T03:59:32.000Z","uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc496bac2336434730f179b1c13298b01fdca78","tid":379912,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:06:57.000Z","msg":"最近壓力好大 <br />\n讀書又好大壓力 好驚自己做唔好<br />\n返parttime又係咁 成日啲我控制唔到既野都入我數<br />\n日日比你罵呢樣果樣 <br />\n開始成日懷疑自己既價值係邊到<br />\n到最近先發現原來身邊果個一直都唔信我 <br />\n覺得我同呢個有路果個有路 <br />\n打去比我啲fd問長問短 <br />\n講真我真係忙到連你都小左見 <br />\n我仲邊有閒情逸致去搞三搞四<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一齊咁耐我對你一直都冇異心 <br />\n只要係我能力範圍內我都願意付出<br />\n又偷偷地睇我電話 話有男仔搵我<br />\n同成年冇見既朋友食飯有男有女既都唔信我<br />\n點解你咁都唔信我 你究竟想我點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知可以同邊個講 個心就好似好多舊大石壓住咁 真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42913fac5cbae74c05f78d528978e9f9d561f6de","tid":379912,"uid":54439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:10:11.000Z","msg":"佢自卑？"},{"pid":"a2e540380c2516bcbe0fa0415f9f7dabd374a1bf","tid":379912,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:10:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6bf6544b80ab3ff2a549f701c7b30ee31ea0e40","tid":379912,"uid":21189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:22:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢自卑？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日剩係懷疑我呢樣果樣 我唔知。"},{"pid":"88fce72aee2d215d92ff7065d13648d0a3608267","tid":379912,"uid":54439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T17:24:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]佢自卑？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日剩係懷疑我呢樣果樣 我唔知。[/quot<br />\n仲係個個ex?"},{"pid":"6b44b5ee6c71719450a01987fa01402d1780225a","tid":3799